OL,3,CFIFA U-turns on water bottle ban at
OL,4,CWorld Cup after backlash
OL,6,FFootball's governing body Fifa, has
OL,7,Fagain amended its water bottle policy
OL,8,Ffor the upcoming World Cup in North
OL,9,FAmerica, allowing fans to bring in one
OL,10,Fsealed, disposable 590ml bottle into
OL,11,Fstadiums.
OL,13,FTicket holders had previously been
OL,14,Fpermitted an empty, transparent and
OL,15,Freusable bottle up to one litre but an
OL,16,Fupdate earlier this week confirmed
OL,17,Freusable bottles were no longer
OL,18,Fpermitted.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
