CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780826741
OL,3,CFIFA U-turns on water bottle ban at
OL,4,CWorld Cup after backlash
OL,6,FThe move was criticised by fan groups
OL,7,Fand scientific experts, who were
OL,8,Falready concerned about the impact of
OL,9,Fextreme heat on the welfare of
OL,10,Fspectators, while Prime Minister Sir
OL,11,FKeir Starmer branded the measure
OL,12,F"wrong" and said it was "about making
OL,13,Fmoney".
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@GO]tD@YOUuD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
