PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780826741
OL,3,CFIFA U-turns on water bottle ban at
OL,4,CWorld Cup after backlash
OL,6,FResponding to the backlash, Fifa has
OL,7,Fnow partially backtracked on the heavy-
OL,8,Fhanded policy, with a post from the
OL,9,FFifa saying: "All fans will be
OL,10,Fpermitted to bring in one, soft,
OL,11,Fplastic, 20-ounce (590ml), factory-
OL,12,Fsealed disposable water bottle into
OL,13,Fany Fifa World Cup 2026 match in the
OL,14,FUSA and Canada."
OL,16,FWorld Cup 2026 chief operating
OL,17,Fofficer, Heimo Schirgi, added: "What
OL,18,Fis not allowed are hard-sided
OL,19,Fresealable water containers, which
OL,20,Fcould pose a safety and security risk."
OL,26,@qD@NOUvD@PO]yD@`OU|D@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
