OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780826741
OL,3,CFIFA U-turns on water bottle ban at
OL,4,CWorld Cup after backlash
OL,6,FFans attending last summer's Club
OL,7,FWorld Cup in the United States had
OL,8,Fbeen permitted to bring empty bottles
OL,9,Fin with them. Water was also on sale
OL,10,Fat Club World Cup stadia, at prices
OL,11,Fbetween #3 and #4.50.
OL,13,FFifa had said on Tuesday the ban's
OL,14,Fpurpose was to "prevent risk and
OL,15,Finjury to players and attendees", but
OL,16,FStarmer told LBC on Friday: "It's just
OL,17,Fwrong. And I can't help but think that
OL,18,Fit's about making money.
OL,26,@vD@POUwD@`O]xD@]OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
