PN,31605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780826741
OL,3,CFIFA U-turns on water bottle ban at
OL,4,CWorld Cup after backlash
OL,6,F"So you can't bring plastic bottles
OL,7,Fin, but you can buy a bottle of water
OL,8,Fwhen you get in the crowd? And then
OL,9,Fit'll be expensive. The tickets
OL,10,Fthemselves cost a fortune, far too
OL,11,Fexpensive in my view.
OL,13,F"The ticket sales are too high. And
OL,14,Fthis is the wrong policy."
