OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780826741
OL,3,CFIFA U-turns on water bottle ban at
OL,4,CWorld Cup after backlash
OL,6,FA Fifa spokesperson said: "Fifa is
OL,7,Fcommitted to protecting the health and
OL,8,Fsafety of all players, referees, fans,
OL,9,Fvolunteers and staff.
OL,11,F"Fifa works closely with each host
OL,12,Fcity committee and local authorities
OL,13,Fon heat mitigation factors for fans
OL,14,Ftravelling to the stadium, which can
OL,15,Finclude resources such as misting
OL,16,Fstations, fans, hydration stations,
OL,17,Fcooling tents and more around the
OL,18,Fstadium footprint.
OL,26,@nD@[OUsD@AOU
